{
  "video_id": "ewzlgnGtfmg",
  "title": "Non-GAAP versus GAAP metrics",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 4720.0,
      "text": "Welcome to the Finance Storyteller series!"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 4720.0,
      "end_time": 6497.0,
      "text": "In this video I am going to discuss"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 6497.0,
      "end_time": 8000.0,
      "text": "GAAP versus non-GAAP metrics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 8000.0,
      "end_time": 10180.0,
      "text": "which is the hottest topic"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 10180.0,
      "end_time": 12180.0,
      "text": "in financial reporting."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 12180.0,
      "end_time": 14526.0,
      "text": "It affects the very core of a company:"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 14526.0,
      "end_time": 17550.0,
      "text": "what is the reality of its financial performance?"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 17550.0,
      "end_time": 20687.0,
      "text": "GAAP versus non-GAAP discussions impact investors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 20687.0,
      "end_time": 23949.0,
      "text": "analysts, financial journalists, company leadership,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 23949.0,
      "end_time": 27039.0,
      "text": "employees, the audit committee and external auditors."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 27039.0,
      "end_time": 31140.0,
      "text": "A lot is at stake here!"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 31140.0,
      "end_time": 33039.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s an overview of how this video is built up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 33039.0,
      "end_time": 34550.0,
      "text": "so you can make your choice of watching"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 34550.0,
      "end_time": 36717.0,
      "text": "it all the way through from beginning to end,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 36717.0,
      "end_time": 38739.0,
      "text": "or jumping straight to the part that is of"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 38739.0,
      "end_time": 40590.0,
      "text": "particular interest to you."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 40590.0,
      "end_time": 43009.0,
      "text": "First section: What does GAAP mean,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 43009.0,
      "end_time": 44460.0,
      "text": "and what is non-GAAP?"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 44460.0,
      "end_time": 47350.0,
      "text": "Basically: why should I care?"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 47350.0,
      "end_time": 48600.0,
      "text": "Second section:"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 48600.0,
      "end_time": 50050.0,
      "text": "What are &quot;common&quot; non-GAAP metrics?"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 50050.0,
      "end_time": 51380.0,
      "text": "What does it look like?"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 51380.0,
      "end_time": 53120.0,
      "text": "Third section:"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 53120.0,
      "end_time": 56180.0,
      "text": "Why are there concerns about non-GAAP reporting?"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 56180.0,
      "end_time": 58140.0,
      "text": "Fourth section:"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 58140.0,
      "end_time": 60380.0,
      "text": "Which guidance have regulators issued"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 60380.0,
      "end_time": 64290.0,
      "text": "to improve transparency?"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 64290.00000000001,
      "end_time": 67382.0,
      "text": "GAAP means Generally Accepted Accounting Principles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 67382.0,
      "end_time": 69820.0,
      "text": "more specifically US GAAP (the accounting"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 69820.0,
      "end_time": 72428.0,
      "text": "standards used in the US) or IFRS"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 72428.0,
      "end_time": 77170.0,
      "text": "(the International Financial Reporting Standards used in"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 77170.0,
      "end_time": 80259.0,
      "text": "126 other countries across the world)."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 80259.0,
      "end_time": 81905.0,
      "text": "Using GAAP provides uniformity"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 81905.0,
      "end_time": 84759.0,
      "text": "in how companies report their financial performance."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 84759.0,
      "end_time": 87311.0,
      "text": "Having accounting standards like US GAAP and IFRS"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 87311.0,
      "end_time": 89290.0,
      "text": "enables you to compare the performance"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 89290.0,
      "end_time": 92914.0,
      "text": "of companies within and across economic sectors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 92914.0,
      "end_time": 95330.0,
      "text": "so the standards are necessarily"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 95330.0,
      "end_time": 96790.0,
      "text": "generic in nature."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 96790.0,
      "end_time": 98646.0,
      "text": "GAAP numbers should be neutral,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 98646.0,
      "end_time": 101940.0,
      "text": "comparable and verifiable, and provide information that"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 101940.0,
      "end_time": 106280.0,
      "text": "markets can trust."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 106280.0,
      "end_time": 108674.0,
      "text": "Non-GAAP metrics are alternative definitions"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 108674.0,
      "end_time": 110960.0,
      "text": "of (in most cases) profitability, that are"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 110960.0,
      "end_time": 113482.0,
      "text": "supposed to enrich the financial information"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 113482.0,
      "end_time": 116520.0,
      "text": "that investors receive about a company&#39;s performance."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 116520.0,
      "end_time": 120648.0,
      "text": "In other words, free-of-charge additional information"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 120648.0,
      "end_time": 123530.0,
      "text": "to provide insights into the company."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 123530.0,
      "end_time": 125796.0,
      "text": "That sounds like ordering steak at a restaurant"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 125796.0,
      "end_time": 127869.0,
      "text": "like you always do, and getting a free side order"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 127869.0,
      "end_time": 130530.0,
      "text": "of vegetables with it."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 130530.0,
      "end_time": 133001.0,
      "text": "Many companies will include a footnote that states"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 133001.0,
      "end_time": 134780.0,
      "text": "that &quot;non-GAAP metrics are useful to"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 134780.0,
      "end_time": 137063.0,
      "text": "investors in their assessment of"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 137063.0,
      "end_time": 138846.0,
      "text": "our operating performance"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 138846.0,
      "end_time": 141230.0,
      "text": "and the valuation of our company&quot;."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 141230.0,
      "end_time": 144503.0,
      "text": "While the steak and vegetables analogy sounds good,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 144503.0,
      "end_time": 146750.0,
      "text": "a better comparison would be to use"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 146750.0,
      "end_time": 148814.0,
      "text": "the classical optical illusion"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 148814.0,
      "end_time": 151360.0,
      "text": "of the old woman and the young woman."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 151360.0,
      "end_time": 153060.0,
      "text": "What do you see?"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 153060.0,
      "end_time": 155970.0,
      "text": "A young woman, an old woman, or can you see both?"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 155970.0,
      "end_time": 157566.0,
      "text": "The young woman is on the left,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 157566.0,
      "end_time": 159557.0,
      "text": "and her gaze seems to be away from us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 159557.0,
      "end_time": 161790.0,
      "text": "facing towards the top left."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 161790.0,
      "end_time": 163750.0,
      "text": "The old woman is in the center,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 163750.0,
      "end_time": 166659.0,
      "text": "with her gaze facing downward and to the left."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 166659.0,
      "end_time": 169899.0,
      "text": "If that is too hard to see, try the duck and the rabbit:"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 169899.0,
      "end_time": 171750.0,
      "text": "is this a drawing of a duck with"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 171750.0,
      "end_time": 173962.0,
      "text": "its beak on the left, or a drawing"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 173962.0,
      "end_time": 176500.0,
      "text": "of a rabbit with its mouth on the right"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 176500.0,
      "end_time": 178349.0,
      "text": "and its ears on the left?"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 178349.0,
      "end_time": 180694.0,
      "text": "Having a company present you with both GAAP"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 180694.0,
      "end_time": 182930.0,
      "text": "and non-GAAP information, is very similar"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 182930.0,
      "end_time": 184292.0,
      "text": "to being asked to spot"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 184292.0,
      "end_time": 186520.0,
      "text": "both perspectives in these drawings!"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 186520.0,
      "end_time": 189078.0,
      "text": "It takes a bit of practice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 189078.0,
      "end_time": 193340.0,
      "text": "and some people are better at it than others."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 193340.0,
      "end_time": 195629.0,
      "text": "How does one spot a non-GAAP metric?"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 195629.0,
      "end_time": 198680.0,
      "text": "Well, the words &quot;adjusted&quot; and &quot;excluding&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 198680.0,
      "end_time": 201730.0,
      "text": "often give it away: adjusted Gross Profit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 201730.0,
      "end_time": 204037.0,
      "text": "adjusted EBITDA, adjusted Net Earnings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 204037.0,
      "end_time": 207290.0,
      "text": "adjusted Earnings Per Share, Operating Profit excluding"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 207290.0,
      "end_time": 210185.0,
      "text": "special items, Net Income excluding"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 210185.0,
      "end_time": 213659.0,
      "text": "non-recurring items, and on and on and on."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 213659.0,
      "end_time": 216200.0,
      "text": "By the way, some companies don&#39;t call"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 216200.0,
      "end_time": 218440.0,
      "text": "non-GAAP information &quot;non-GAAP&quot;,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 218440.0,
      "end_time": 220700.0,
      "text": "but speak of core profitability"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 220700.0,
      "end_time": 223226.0,
      "text": "normalized profitability,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 223226.0,
      "end_time": 227720.0,
      "text": "underlying profitability, or &quot;pro forma&quot; measures."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 227720.0,
      "end_time": 230011.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s an example of a company that provides"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 230011.0,
      "end_time": 232510.0,
      "text": "a list of non-operational items that it excludes"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 232510.0,
      "end_time": 236484.0,
      "text": "to get to adjusted EBITDA and adjusted EPS:"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 236484.0,
      "end_time": 238610.0,
      "text": "Verizon Communications."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 238610.0,
      "end_time": 242607.0,
      "text": "Its profitability according to GAAP was unusually low"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 242607.0,
      "end_time": 245549.0,
      "text": "in 2012 and 2014, and unusually high in"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 245549.0,
      "end_time": 249060.0,
      "text": "2013 and 2015, mostly due to unusual charges"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 249060.0,
      "end_time": 252730.0,
      "text": "or credits in an operating expense line called"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 252730.0,
      "end_time": 256000.0,
      "text": "&quot;Severance, Pension and Benefit&quot;."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 256000.0,
      "end_time": 258869.0,
      "text": "It was a very significant charge (or extra cost)"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 258869.00000000003,
      "end_time": 261140.00000000003,
      "text": "in the range of 6 to 7 billion dollars"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 261140.0,
      "end_time": 266437.0,
      "text": "in 2012 and 2014, and a very significant credit"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 266437.0,
      "end_time": 270720.0,
      "text": "(or &quot;negative cost&quot;) in 2013 and 2015."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 270720.0,
      "end_time": 273652.0,
      "text": "If I want to do a long-term trend analysis as an investor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 273652.0,
      "end_time": 275270.0,
      "text": "it is useful to have the company"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 275270.0,
      "end_time": 277178.0,
      "text": "provide me with these numbers"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 277178.0,
      "end_time": 280270.0,
      "text": "to &quot;normalize&quot; the trend and exclude the noise."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 280270.0,
      "end_time": 282552.0,
      "text": "Verizon is a very profitable company,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 282552.0,
      "end_time": 284877.0,
      "text": "both under GAAP and non-GAAP metrics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 284877.0,
      "end_time": 285820.0,
      "text": "and adjustments from GAAP to non-GAAP"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 285820.0,
      "end_time": 290000.0,
      "text": "can go either way: results can become higher or lower"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 290000.0,
      "end_time": 295280.0,
      "text": "when unusual items are excluded."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 295280.0,
      "end_time": 297069.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s a second example:"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 297069.0,
      "end_time": 299380.0,
      "text": "pharmaceutical company Valeant."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 299380.0,
      "end_time": 301712.0,
      "text": "In their overview of non-GAAP adjustments"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 301712.0,
      "end_time": 304100.0,
      "text": "to get from the GAAP net income at the top"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 304100.0,
      "end_time": 307014.0,
      "text": "to the non-GAAP net income at the bottom,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 307014.0,
      "end_time": 310000.0,
      "text": "Valeant has a long list of up to 15 items,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 310000.0,
      "end_time": 313592.0,
      "text": "and every year the non-GAAP results are higher"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 313592.0,
      "end_time": 315310.0,
      "text": "than the GAAP results."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 315310.0,
      "end_time": 319764.0,
      "text": "In 2015, the company had a GAAP loss of $292 million"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 319764.0,
      "end_time": 322590.0,
      "text": "but an &quot;adjusted&quot; non-GAAP profit"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 322590.0,
      "end_time": 325086.0,
      "text": "of $2.8 billion after stripping out"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 325086.0,
      "end_time": 329080.0,
      "text": "amortization of intangible assets, acquisition costs and"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 329080.0,
      "end_time": 330120.0,
      "text": "other expenses."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 330120.0,
      "end_time": 332591.0,
      "text": "On a revenue of $10.4 billion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 332591.0,
      "end_time": 335700.0,
      "text": "that means the GAAP net profit margin"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 335700.0,
      "end_time": 337940.0,
      "text": "of -3% has turned"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 337940.0,
      "end_time": 341450.0,
      "text": "into a non-GAAP profit margin of +27%."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 341450.0,
      "end_time": 344380.0,
      "text": "Quite a difference!"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 344380.0,
      "end_time": 346557.0,
      "text": "So why should anyone worry about"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 346557.0,
      "end_time": 349210.0,
      "text": "the proliferation of non-GAAP measures?"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 349210.0,
      "end_time": 351591.0,
      "text": "There are four main reasons for that:"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 351591.0,
      "end_time": 354230.0,
      "text": "First of all, non-GAAP financial measures"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 354230.0,
      "end_time": 356100.0,
      "text": "are not audited!"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 356100.0,
      "end_time": 358337.0,
      "text": "The leadership of companies could be tempted"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 358337.0,
      "end_time": 360980.0,
      "text": "to behave in a more opportunistic way in classifying"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 360980.0,
      "end_time": 365050.0,
      "text": "results and defining metrics of success."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 365050.0,
      "end_time": 367082.0,
      "text": "Second: more and more companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 367082.0,
      "end_time": 369621.0,
      "text": "are using non-GAAP financial measures,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 369621.0,
      "end_time": 371480.0,
      "text": "which defeats the purpose"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 371480.0,
      "end_time": 373588.0,
      "text": "of the word &quot;General&quot; in the term"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 373588.0,
      "end_time": 376410.0,
      "text": "Generally Accepted Accounting Principles."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 376410.0,
      "end_time": 378332.0,
      "text": "The Wall Street Journal recently reported"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 378332.0,
      "end_time": 380770.0,
      "text": "that only 6 percent of companies in the S&amp;P500 index"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 380770.0,
      "end_time": 388100.0,
      "text": "reported 2015 financials using solely GAAP measures."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 388100.0,
      "end_time": 391887.0,
      "text": "According to research firm Audit Analytics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 391887.0,
      "end_time": 394970.0,
      "text": "this figure was 25 percent in 2006."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 394970.0,
      "end_time": 397393.0,
      "text": "Third: analysts and the media"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 397393.0,
      "end_time": 401070.0,
      "text": "have given non-GAAP metrics more prominence."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 401070.0,
      "end_time": 403860.0,
      "text": "Fourth and perhaps most concerning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 403860.0,
      "end_time": 406480.0,
      "text": "non-GAAP results are very often better"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 406480.0,
      "end_time": 408520.0,
      "text": "than those reported under GAAP!"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 408520.0,
      "end_time": 410020.0,
      "text": "And the spread between them has been growing."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 410020.0,
      "end_time": 413472.0,
      "text": "S&amp;P published a study of FTSE100 companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 413472.0,
      "end_time": 417500.0,
      "text": "showing that around 80% of the companies reported"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 417500.0,
      "end_time": 420656.0,
      "text": "an adjusted operating profit that was higher"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 420656.0,
      "end_time": 423310.0,
      "text": "than the unadjusted operating profit."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 423310.0,
      "end_time": 425957.0,
      "text": "So the big question is: how do we avoid"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 425957.0,
      "end_time": 427754.0,
      "text": "non-GAAP measures becoming"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 427754.0,
      "end_time": 429690.0,
      "text": "&quot;Earnings Before Bad Stuff&quot;?"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 429690.0,
      "end_time": 432744.0,
      "text": "Fortunately, the issue is in the spotlight"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 432744.0,
      "end_time": 434780.0,
      "text": "with regulatory agencies and"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 434780.0,
      "end_time": 435786.0,
      "text": "accounting standards boards,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 435786.0,
      "end_time": 436900.0,
      "text": "all the way up to the chairmen!"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 436900.0,
      "end_time": 440289.0,
      "text": "They have made some very clear statements"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 440289.0,
      "end_time": 441860.0,
      "text": "about the concerns:"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 441860.0,
      "end_time": 443977.0,
      "text": "Securities and Exchange Commission"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 443977.0,
      "end_time": 445970.0,
      "text": "Chairman Mary Jo White has said:"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 445970.0,
      "end_time": 448924.0,
      "text": "&quot;Non-GAAP information is meant to supplement"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 448924.0,
      "end_time": 451810.0,
      "text": "the GAAP information, but not supplant it.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 451810.0,
      "end_time": 455560.0,
      "text": "and &quot;In too many cases, the non-GAAP information"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 455560.0,
      "end_time": 459860.0,
      "text": "has become the key message to investors.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 459860.0,
      "end_time": 461060.0,
      "text": "Hans Hoogervorst"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 461060.0,
      "end_time": 464420.0,
      "text": "(Chairman of the International Accounting Standards Board,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 464420.0,
      "end_time": 465810.0,
      "text": "in charge of IFRS) said:"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 465810.0,
      "end_time": 467926.0,
      "text": "&quot;Non-GAAP measures represent"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 467926.0,
      "end_time": 469740.0,
      "text": "a selective presentation"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 469740.0,
      "end_time": 471730.0,
      "text": "of an entity&#39;s financial performance."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 471730.0,
      "end_time": 475940.0,
      "text": "Often, that selection is not free from bias.&quot; and"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 475940.0,
      "end_time": 478076.0,
      "text": "&quot;We have found quite a few examples"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 478076.0,
      "end_time": 480867.0,
      "text": "of financial reporting where the IFRS numbers"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 480867.0,
      "end_time": 482600.0,
      "text": "are overshadowed"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 482600.0,
      "end_time": 483970.0,
      "text": "by non-GAAP measures."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 483970.0,
      "end_time": 485333.0,
      "text": "In some cases,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 485333.0,
      "end_time": 490300.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s really difficult to find the net income line.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 490300.0,
      "end_time": 493247.0,
      "text": "Not only have representatives of regulatory agencies"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 493247.0,
      "end_time": 495400.0,
      "text": "and accounting standards boards voiced"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 495400.0,
      "end_time": 498640.0,
      "text": "their concerns, they are taking active steps"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 498640.0,
      "end_time": 501880.0,
      "text": "to reverse the trend of non-GAAP prominence."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 501880.0,
      "end_time": 503851.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s remember the overarching principle"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 503851.0,
      "end_time": 506020.0,
      "text": "of financial reporting: financial statements"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 506020.0,
      "end_time": 508591.0,
      "text": "should be a &quot;fair and accurate representation&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 508591.0,
      "end_time": 511050.0,
      "text": "of the company&#39;s financial position,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 511050.0,
      "end_time": 513550.0,
      "text": "results of operations and cash flows."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 513549.99999999994,
      "end_time": 516101.99999999994,
      "text": "For both GAAP and non-GAAP information,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 516102.0,
      "end_time": 518000.0,
      "text": "another key principle is that"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 518000.0,
      "end_time": 520610.0,
      "text": "information cannot be misleading."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 520610.0,
      "end_time": 522630.0,
      "text": "The active steps that are being taken"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 522630.0,
      "end_time": 523880.0,
      "text": "can be at the individual company level,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 523880.0,
      "end_time": 526260.0,
      "text": "with the SEC sending more comment letters"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 526260.0,
      "end_time": 528530.0,
      "text": "to companies questioning their use"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 528530.0,
      "end_time": 530460.0,
      "text": "of non-GAAP metrics."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 530460.0,
      "end_time": 533593.0,
      "text": "On the aggregate level, the SEC has issued"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 533593.0,
      "end_time": 535830.0,
      "text": "formal guidance on this topic."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 535830.0,
      "end_time": 538928.0,
      "text": "Here are some striking examples of that guidance:"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 538928.0,
      "end_time": 541710.0,
      "text": "A non-GAAP measure that is adjusted only for"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 541710.0,
      "end_time": 543942.0,
      "text": "non-recurring charges when there were"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 543942.0,
      "end_time": 545969.0,
      "text": "non-recurring gains that occurred"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 545969.0,
      "end_time": 547740.0,
      "text": "during the same period"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 547740.0,
      "end_time": 550000.0,
      "text": "could violate Rule 100(b) of Regulation G"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 550000.0,
      "end_time": 553603.0,
      "text": "When a registrant presents a non-GAAP measure"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 553603.0,
      "end_time": 555260.0,
      "text": "it must present"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 555260.0,
      "end_time": 558219.0,
      "text": "the most directly comparable GAAP measure"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 558219.0,
      "end_time": 560810.0,
      "text": "with equal or greater prominence"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 560810.0,
      "end_time": 563373.0,
      "text": "- in this element of the guidance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 563373.0,
      "end_time": 565600.0,
      "text": "the SEC really spells it out:"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 565600.0,
      "end_time": 567520.0,
      "text": "do not present a non-GAAP measure"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 567520.0,
      "end_time": 570024.0,
      "text": "using a style of presentation"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 570024.0,
      "end_time": 573340.0,
      "text": "(such as bold or larger font) that emphasizes the"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 573340.0,
      "end_time": 575181.0,
      "text": "non-GAAP measure over the"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 575181.0,
      "end_time": 576977.0,
      "text": "comparable GAAP measure;"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 576977.0,
      "end_time": 579820.0,
      "text": "do not place a non-GAAP measure before"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 579820.0,
      "end_time": 582881.0,
      "text": "the most directly comparable GAAP measure;"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 582881.0,
      "end_time": 585870.0,
      "text": "do not include only a non-GAAP measure in"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 585870.0,
      "end_time": 589110.0,
      "text": "an earnings release headline."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 589110.0,
      "end_time": 591570.0,
      "text": "Explain what is the purpose of the non-GAAP measure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 591570.0,
      "end_time": 593320.0,
      "text": "and why management believes investors"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 593320.0,
      "end_time": 596300.0,
      "text": "would find the non-GAAP measure useful."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 596300.0,
      "end_time": 598050.0,
      "text": "Improvement is underway."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 598050.0,
      "end_time": 602120.0,
      "text": "Among the S&amp;P 500 companies reporting results"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 602120.0,
      "end_time": 606100.0,
      "text": "since the start of July 2016, 81% have given"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 606100.0,
      "end_time": 608831.0,
      "text": "prominence to GAAP figures, an increase from"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 608831.0,
      "end_time": 611810.0,
      "text": "the 52% that did so when reporting first-quarter"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 611810.0,
      "end_time": 614936.0,
      "text": "results, according to an Audit Analytics analysis"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 614936.0,
      "end_time": 617360.0,
      "text": "conducted for The Wall Street Journal."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 617360.0,
      "end_time": 619770.0,
      "text": "I hope this was helpful."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 619770.0,
      "end_time": 621250.0,
      "text": "Thank you for watching!"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 621250.0,
      "end_time": 622287.0,
      "text": "Please subscribe to"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 622287.0,
      "end_time": 624470.0,
      "text": "the Finance Storyteller YouTube channel."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 624470.0,
      "end_time": 634470.0,
      "text": "More videos coming soon!"
    }
  ]
}